hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 2.1-2.6 難到仆街, K map 又唔識點做</blockquote><br />\nk map唔難<br />\n寫幾粒數字 畫幾個圈 就做完<br />\n好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔識點睇，同埋點約到最簡"},{"pid":"f0f81de6effdb40f360356b97ee4ae4ae2204e09","tid":51934,"uid":56627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T18:32:52.000Z","msg":"樓主自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea66e31fb2d7b91b632814cf0f92e49049c54d40","tid":51934,"uid":54735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T18:36:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fbe3bfd8534c9c19f6bfd1748b6c890a41101394","tid":51934,"uid":65526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T18:41:06.000Z","msg":"你邊間😂相認下"},{"pid":"2c39103af30e9890faa64730282b2ffd420e68fa","tid":51934,"uid":12335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T18:42:51.000Z","msg":"青大year2留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b37ad33c5d4118e98e46fab05c22a5434417553","tid":51934,"uid":54049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T18:49:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 2.1-2.6 難到仆街, K map 又唔識點做</blockquote><br />\nk map唔難<br />\n寫幾粒數字 畫幾個圈 就做完<br />\n好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔識點睇，同埋點約到最簡</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果要格硬用三兩句講晒 k map做法就係<br />\n<br />\n將truth table 用2d 既形式表達出黎<br />\n將痴埋一齊既圈起佢<br />\n再係每個圈撈不變既野出黎加埋佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然仲有少少細節要留意 <br />\n例如圈既大小限制 有bar定冇 bar 呀之類<br />\n不過基本上就係咁做"},{"pid":"a5ea153ddf5dd1ffde5d09477d52986949197e4c","tid":51934,"uid":54049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T18:58:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>最撚憎啲成績好就串串共既仆街，唔知樓主係咪</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我以前都比班所謂精英班d仆街仔串得多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過而家諗下諗下<span style=\"color: red;\">有成績唔等如有實力</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有實力自然有成績架啦(我諗)<br />\n有實力果d咪串得起囉 冇既就收皮<br />\n不過我兩樣都冇既 都係算鳩數把啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n發覺好多學渣都鍾意用呢句野嚟自慰</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自慰好呀<br />\n人始終係需要好好比個機會比自己合理化自己既行為架嘛 <br />\n尤其是當做左d好奇怪既決定/事果陣<br />\n如果唔係好容易會懷疑自己 到時真係後悔搞到個人頹晒就無畏啦 唔做都做左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過認真咁諗其實成績都係入場劵黎架姐<br />\n入完場 撈唔撈得掂都好緊要架嘛<br />\n有料既咪撈得掂就happy幾年<br />\n冇既咪撈唔掂就頹足幾年/quit 話唔埋仲晒左一大筆錢 何必呢<br />\n見過唔少鳩chur讀書高分入u結果過得好辛苦+sad<br />\n唔想步佢地後塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申自認唔算學渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"757e78192ca337b2e166b46f856fdba9090a6d4d","tid":51934,"uid":54049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T19:01:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你邊間😂相認下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可唔可以唔相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n疑似已經比人認左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好柒呀我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}